          <h1>We understand</h1>
          <p>As we all well know, to achieve fluency in a foreign language, regular practice and peserverance is key but life can get in the way!</p>
          <p>So what if we told you if you could immerse yourself from the comfort of your own home and fit it in around other competing priorities?</p>
          <p>Our six month language learning bootcamp gives you all the tools you need to develop fluency in Chinese fully equipped to continue learning beyond the course independently if you wish. The short-term intensive nature of the course, with our experts to guide you, will save you years of time and frustration so very much a worthy investment if you are serious about becoming fluent in a language.</p>
          <h2>Course Overview</h2>
          <p>Learners complete online exercises during interactive Zoom sessions three times per week.</p>
          <p>During the Zoom sessions, the teacher gives general feedback to the group based on exercise submissions across all skill areas. TAs (Teaching Assistants) are also available to help you with any one-to-one queries and for further practice.</p>
          <p>Students also go into breakout rooms for 'structured production' sessions. They can choose to either:
            <ul>
              <li>Prepare an oral presentation based on the writing text they produced during the online exercises</li>
              <li>Prepare an oral presentation based on the existing reading text given for that day's online exercises</li>
              <li>Prepare an oral dialogue with their breakout room buddy in Chinese</li>
            </ul>
            <p>At the end of the session, TAs may recommend and encourage groups, pairs or individuals to perform their presentations or dialogues to the rest of the group to celebrate the fruits of their learning for the day and to obtain feedback.</p>
            <p>Benefits of the breakout room/buddy system:
              <ul>
                <li>In it together - students can help each other learn and make friends along the way</li>
                <li>Students can practise Chinese conversation with each other</li>
                <li>TAs can pop into the rooms to help with any questions</li>
                <li>Students can create tickets to practise with a TA or to ask questions</li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                <p>Our groundbreaking language learning bootcamp is guaranteed to help you to succeed. We look forward to joining us on an unforgettable journey. You can do it!</p>
